# Security Headers
<IfModule mod_headers.c>
    Header set X-Frame-Options "DENY"
    Header set X-Content-Type-Options "nosniff"
    Header set Referrer-Policy "strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
    Header set Content-Security-Policy "default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' https://cdn.jsdelivr.net; style-src 'self' https://fonts.googleapis.com; font-src https://fonts.gstatic.com; img-src 'self' https://github.com https://raw.githubusercontent.com https://avatars.githubusercontent.com; connect-src 'self' https://api.github.com"
</IfModule>
